#. Tag: title
#: vfs.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Virtual file systems (VFS)"
msgstr "Navidezni datotečni sistemi (VFS)"

#. Tag: primary
#: vfs.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>VFS</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>VFS</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A basic <link linkend=\"features\">OFM feature</link> is VFS, this an "
"abstracted layer over all kinds of archived information (ZIP files, &FTP; "
"servers, TAR archives, &NFS; filesystems, SAMBA shares, ISO &CD;/&DVD; "
"images, RPM catalogs, &etc;), which allows the user to access all the "
"information in these divergent types of filesystems transparently - just "
"like entering an ordinary sub-folder. &krusader; supports several virtual "
"file systems:"
msgstr ""
"Osnovna <link linkend=\"features\">funkcija OFM</link> je VFS, to je "
"abstrahirana plast nad vsemi vrstami arhiviranih informacij (datoteke ZIP, "
"&FTP; strežniki, arhivi TAR, &NFS; datotečni sistemi, delitve SAMBA, ISO "
"&CD; /&DVD; slike, katalogi RPM &etc;), ki uporabniku omogoča pregleden "
"dostop do vseh informacij v teh različnih vrstah datotečnih sistemov - tako "
"kot bi vstopil v običajno podmapo. &krusader; podpira več virtualnih "
"datotečnih sistemov:"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote connections VFS</link>: provides "
"the capability of working with a remote connection session (&FTP;, &NFS;, "
"Samba, FISH, SFTP) like with local filesystems. It is perfect for complex "
"remote operations and almost as powerful as most standalone &GUI; remote "
"clients."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Oddaljene povezave VFS</link>: nudi "
"zmožnost dela z oddaljeno povezovalno sejo (&FTP;, &NFS;, Samba, FISH, SFTP) "
"kot z lokalnimi datotečnimi sistemi. Popoln je za zapletene operacije na "
"daljavo in skoraj tako zmogljiv kot večina samostojnih &GUI; oddaljene "
"stranke."

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Archive VFS</link>: allows to browse archives in "
"VFS as it was a folder (ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, tar, "
"zip and 7-zip)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Arhiv VFS</link>: omogoča brskanje po arhivih v "
"VFS, kot je bila mapa (ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, rpm, tar, "
"zip in 7 -zip)."

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Search VFS</link>: <guibutton>Feed to listbox</"
"guibutton> places the search results in VFS."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Iskanje VFS</link>: <guibutton>Vir v polje s "
"seznamom</guibutton> postavi rezultate iskanja v VFS."

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer VFS</link>: places the "
"synchronizer results in VFS."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">VFS sinhronizatorja</link>: postavi rezultate "
"sinhronizatorja v VFS."

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Actions you perform on the files in VFS are performed on the 'real' files. "
"You do not just delete files from the VFS - you delete them from your hard "
"drive. Limitations: you cannot create folders inside a VFS."
msgstr ""
"Dejanja, ki jih izvajate na datotekah v VFS, se izvajajo na 'pravih' "
"datotekah. Datotek ne izbrišete samo iz VFS - izbrišete jih s trdega diska. "
"Omejitve: ne morete ustvarjati map znotraj VFS."

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to keep the folder structure when doing a copy from a virtual "
"folder to a non virtual folder, by selecting the <quote>Keep virtual folder "
"structure</quote> check box of the copy dialog. Imagine the following "
"virtual folder: <screen><prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>file:/home/myhome/"
"mydir1/myfile1</userinput></screen> <screen><prompt>$</prompt> "
"<userinput>file:/home/myhome/mydir1/myfile2</userinput></screen> "
"<screen><prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>file:/home/myhome/mydir2/myfile3</"
"userinput></screen> Then do the following steps:"
msgstr ""
"Strukturo mape lahko obdržite pri kopiranju iz navidezne mape v nenavidezno "
"mapo, tako da izberete potrditveno polje <quote>Ohrani strukturo navidezne "
"mape</quote> v pogovornem oknu za kopiranje. Predstavljajte si naslednjo "
"virtualno mapo: <screen><prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>file:/home/myhome/"
"mydir1/myfile1</userinput></screen> <screen><prompt>$</prompt> "
"<userinput>datoteka:/home/myhome/mydir1/myfile2</userinput></screen> "
"<screen><prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>file:/home/myhome/mydir2/myfile3</"
"userinput></screen> Nato naredite naslednje korake:"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "go to the virtual folder and select the files"
msgstr "pojdite v virtualno mapo in izberite datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "select a destination folder (non virtual!)"
msgstr "izberite ciljno mapo (ne virtualno!)"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "press <keycap>F5</keycap>-&gt; copy dialog appears"
msgstr ""
"pritisnite <keycap>F5</keycap>-&gt; prikaže se pogovorno okno za kopiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check <guilabel>Keep virtual folder structure</guilabel>"
msgstr "Označite <guilabel>Ohrani strukturo navidezne mape</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select <filename>/home/myhome/</filename> for base &URL;"
msgstr "Izberite <filename>/dom/mojdom/</filename> za osnovni &URL;"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start copy by pressing OK"
msgstr "Zaženite kopiranje s pritiskom na OK"

#. Tag: para
#: vfs.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "The result will be:"
msgstr "Rezultat bo:"

#. Tag: screen
#: vfs.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir1/myfile1</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir1/myfile1</userinput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: vfs.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir1/myfile2</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir1/myfile2</userinput>"

#. Tag: screen
#: vfs.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir2/myfile3</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>$</prompt> <userinput>destinationdir/mydir2/myfile3</userinput>"
